abstract: Wrangling between Time Warner Cable and the NFL Network persists, with Time Warner still refusing to carry the network eight years after its birth; revenue sharing is at the core of the long-running dispute.
snippet: Eight years after the NFL Network’s birth, Time Warner Cable still won’t show it.
lead_paragraph: Eight years after the NFL Network’s birth, Time Warner Cable still won’t show it.

headline.main: The NFL Network and Time Warner Continue to Spar
